      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's been so long since i've actually spoken to anyone in person. sometimes i'm sitting in this cafe just watching people walk by and it hits me that i could just... not be here anymore, and the world wouldn't even stutter. like my whole life is just a zero-sum game. i'm just taking up space that doesn't even matter.",
